---
title: Crumbed Hoki & Veggie Fries with Avocado Salad & Herby Mayo
description: Dive into a sea of flavour with our crumbed hoki and veggie fries, where crispy fish fillets and veggie fries take a dip in a pool of zesty excitement! Catch the delicious drift with a dollop of dill-parsley mayo, making every bite a tasty adventure that'll have your taste buds doing the happy dance!
